nodes.text: This factory was located on an Outer Rim planet controlled by the Confederacy of Independent Systems.

During the Clone Wars, this factory was raided by the Galactic Republic in an attempt to steal an encrypted file held on a data chip, one crucial to the Separatists' war effort. The encrypted file contained the plans of a new model of battle droid that was designed in an intent to replace the B1-Series battle droid in the Droid Army.
